&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional stakeholders (including Product, Engineering and Operations) to support requirement definition, testing activities, and the maintenance of AFC program documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in monitoring regulatory developments and contribute to the implementation of AFC compliance enhancements where required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
