&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the first point of contact for our users via live chat and tickets — always keeping your communication clear, friendly, and fast.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help customers solve everyday issues and make their Bitpanda journey smooth, positive, and stress-free.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share feedback and ideas with the team to improve the way we support our users and make the customer journey even better.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work towards team goals like fast response times and high customer satisfaction while staying up to date with Bitpanda’s products and features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be flexible with a shift-based schedule (including evenings and weekends) — planned in advance so you can balance work and life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re an &lt;strong&gt;empathetic and friendly communicator&lt;/strong&gt; who enjoys helping people and can stay calm, reliable, and positive even when things get busy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You speak &lt;strong&gt;fluent English and German &lt;/strong&gt;and other EU language is an advantage&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re curious about &lt;strong&gt;fintech, investing, or crypto&lt;/strong&gt; and excited to learn more (bonus points if you already know your way around crypto wallets, DEXs, or trading).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re detail-oriented, dependable, and comfortable juggling multiple chats at once while still delivering &lt;strong&gt;clear, high-quality answers&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in a &lt;strong&gt;fast-paced, international environment&lt;/strong&gt; and love working as part of a team.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt

