&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;French &lt;/strong&gt;(C2 level or equivalent) and English (B2 level or higher); additional languages are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for crypto, investing, and an interest in global financial markets or fintech domains is advantageous but optional.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible and adaptable to thrive in a dynamic, fast-paced environment; willing to work in shift patterns, including evenings and weekends, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Customer Care systems, such as Zendesk, is desirable but optional.&lt;/li&gt;
