&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Driven Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage Agentic AI, LLMs, and frameworks (like AWS Bedrock) to build internal tools for automated vulnerability detection and secret scanning (e.g., detecting leaked PII or security misconfigurations).&lt;/li&gt;
